    <note>Fu(5) Taishiren [5259] Liu Yizhi, WJ, 51.11b-15b. She was married before to Xinchang county resident, Shi(4). CBD, 5, 3880.Hartwell原另建有Fu(5) Taishiren(2) [5412] 條，注作：Liu Yizhi, WJ, 51.12b-15b Has information on jiafa; she was well-educated at age 18--this was second marriage after marrying a Shi(4). CBD, 5, 3858-9.但是按劉一止所作《太碩人傅氏墓誌銘》知傅氏為劉一止伯父繼妻，而非再嫁于劉氏。且傅氏丈夫當爲劉握，而劉述為劉握父。而數據庫中已有劉握妻傅氏條，本條刪除。</note>
